(7, 674, 'Alex', 'juliemcnaughtan@gmail.com', 'https://cannabissafetyinstitute.org/', '207.180.255.81', '2020-04-19 07:43:52', '2020-04-19 07:43:52', 'After looking over a few of the blog posts on your \r\nsite, I really like your way of writing a blog.\r\nI added it to my bookmark webpage list and will be checking back soon. Please check \r\nout my web site too and let me know what you think.', 0, '0', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; rv:52.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/52.0 SeaMonkey/2.49.3', '', 0, 0),
